      • ParameterMatcher

        public ParameterMatcher​(java.lang.String commandRegex,
                        java.util.Map<hu.zza.clim.menu.Position,​ParameterPattern> patternMap)
        Creates a ParameterMatcher object with simple commandRegex (without flags) and without setting processable text initially.

        While many different input regexes can be set using different ParameterPattern objects, the command regex should be uniform and universal.

        Parameters:
        commandRegex - same as regex in Pattern.compile(String)
        patternMap - Map of Position - ParameterPattern bindings
        Since:
        0.1
